<H3> <TI>   Berov Discharged, Declared `Fit for Work' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Berov Discharged, Declared `Fit for Work' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0804170094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1600 
GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0804170094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Today the group of consultants treating Prime 
Minister Lyuben Berov decided to discharge the prime minister 
from the hospital because his hospital treatment has been 
successfully concluded. The condition of the prime minister's 
cardiovascular system has been stabilized, and it is the view of 
the consultants that the prime minister is fit for work. 

</TEXT>

