BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 11 Apr--President Lech Walesa received at 
the Belweder today Bulgarian Foreign Minister Stanislav 
Daskalov, who is paying an official two-day visit to Poland. 
  "For many years, we were in the same political and economic 
orbit, and certain bonds and cooperation were established. Now, 
when we are reforming our countries, I think we should return to 
