<F P=105> Slovak </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] Strobe Talbott, the U.S. deputy secretary of 
state, began a one-day visit to Slovakia this morning. [passage 
omitted] 
  This morning, Talbott met President Michal Kovac. Agatha 
Stanekova reports. [passage omitted] 
  [Begin Stanekova recording] The first point on the agenda of 
Talbott's visit to Slovakia was the reception by Slovak 
President Kovac at Primacialny Palace in Bratislava. 
