<H3> <TI>   Churkin Meets With Karadzic in Pale </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Churkin Meets With Karadzic in Pale </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1104170994 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1641 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1104170994 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Sarajevo, 11 April (TANJUG) -- Vitaliy Churkin, 
Russian deputy foreign minister and the Russian president's 
special envoy to the former Yugoslavia, arrived in Pale from 
Belgrade this evening. 
  Immediately after that, at around 1820, Churkin met with 
Srpska republic president Radovan Karadzic. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

