<H4>    Serreqi Sees Integration as `Priority' </H4>

<F P=102> AU0804105894 Tirana ATA in English 0820 GMT 8 Apr 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU0804105894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


