<H3> <TI>   ODS Favors Redressing Wrongs Inflicted on Jews </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ODS Favors Redressing Wrongs Inflicted on Jews </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1204101394 Prague CTK in English 2058 GMT 11 Apr 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU1204101394 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague CTK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Prague, April 11 (CTK) -- The Civic Democratic 
Party (ODS) Executive Council, in a resolution adopted at its 
meeting today, confirmed its will to redress property wrongs 
inflicted on Jews who did not receive their property because of 
political changes in February 1948 and whose property currently 
belongs to the state, ODS Deputy Chairman Jan Strasky told 
journalists. 
  The Executive Council supports the adoption of a law to 
right 
the injustices inflicted on Jewish people, Strasky said. 
  He said that the Executive Council discussed a proposal by 
the Christian Democratic Union-Czechoslovak People's Party 
(KDU-CSL) concerning the restitution of church property, 
currently in the state's possession. 
  The Council had asked ODS ministers and deputies to take a 
positive stand on such a bill provided an agreement on a 
limitation or restriction of restitutions of land and forests 
was achieved and that is was agreed that this bill would be the 
final one redressing property wrongs inflicted on the Church, 
Strasky said. 

</TEXT>

