  [Excerpt] President Michal Kovac received Strobe Talbott, 
U.S. deputy secretary of state, in Bratislava today. 
  President Kovac informed Talbott about the current political 
situation in Slovakia and highlighted our interest in being 
integrated into the political, economic, and security structures 
of the West, on the premise that both Russia and Ukraine respect 
this decision. [passage omitted] 

