  [Text] Fresh forces of the chetnik formations have arrived 
in [word indistinct] Ustipraca, (?Luksici) and [words 
indistinct]. They are being accompanied by armored-mechanized 
units of the former Yugoslav Peoples' Army. [Words indistinct] 
the free territory, from mortars and antiaircraft arms the 
chetniks are pounding the town's settlements of Vidkovici, 
[words indistinct], while from the right bank of the Drina River 
they are systematically firing at apartment after apartment, 
house after house, with snipers 80 [word indistinct]. For this 
reason we ask for an immediate intervention so that this town 
will not turn into the biggest grave in the history of mankind. 
  The latest information claims that Karadzic's fascists are 
concentrating additional forces in (?Leskici), Ustipraca, and 
(?Luksici) and that in the planning of a new powerful offensive 
