<F P=100> ALBANIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Government Orders Greek Consul To Leave </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Orders Greek Consul To Leave </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1204155294 Tirana Radio Tirana Network in Albanian 1430 
GMT 12 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1204155294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana Radio Tirana Network </F>
<F P=105>  Albanian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Albanian Government at noon today declared 
Khristos Iakovou, Greek general consul in Gjirokaster, persona 
non grata. The decision was officially stated in a note to 
Greek Ambassador in Tirana Tsalikis. 
  The note from the Albanian Foreign Ministry states that the 
decision to expel the Greek consul was based on activities not 
in accordance with his duties in our country. He is obliged to 
leave the Republic of Albania within 48 hours from the time of 
the official note's delivery. 

</TEXT>

