  [Text] Prague, April 12 (CTK) -- Deputy Foreign Minister 
Alexandr Vondra told the North Atlantic Assembly (NAA) 
representatives visiting the country that the Czech government 
is shortly to debate a document expounding its conception of 
cooperation with NATO in the framework of the Partnership for 
