Chairman Loic Bouvard and Secretary- General Peter Corterier. 
  Parliamentary Chairman Milan Uhde told journalists it was a 
huge lesson in solidarity that the Czech Republic, although 
feeling threatened by no country, was intensively interested in 
collective European security. 

